Veio sozinho?

154
00:17:02,883 --> 00:17:04,382
Não.

155
00:17:07,728 --> 00:17:09,500
Relaxem.

156
00:17:35,787 --> 00:17:38,244
Eu só pensei que,
como homens,

157
00:17:38,245 --> 00:17:40,190
